  <title translate="true">The Working Area</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para style="margin-bottom:10px; line-height:2.0;"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">The Working Area</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Working Area</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> is used to display and edit the model.  All objects are created and edited in the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Working Area</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">.  It is also possible to edit the grid in the Working Area.  The </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Zoom</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">&#32;</text><image src="Zoom.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">Zoom button</title></image><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Zoom In</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">&#32;</text><image src="ZoomIn.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">Zoom In button</title></image><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Zoom Out</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">&#32;</text><image src="ZoomOut.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">Zoom Out button</title></image><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, and </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Pan</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">&#32;</text><image src="Pan.PNG" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">Pan button</title></image><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> buttons allow the user to navigate in the Working Area. The menu command </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Navigation|Restore Default 2-D View</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> will zoom in or out so that most or all of the grid or mesh is visible in the top, front, and side views. &#160;See the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Grid2" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Grid</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Mesh" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Mesh</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Object2" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Object</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, and </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="View" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">View</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> menu items under </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Main_Menu_and_Buttons" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Main Menu and Buttons</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> for more details.</text></para>
  </body>
